title: BRIEF-Tag Oil Q3 Average Net Daily Production 1,043 BOE/d, Down 9 Pct From Q2
text: February 14, 2018 / 3:02 PM / in 33 minutes BRIEF-Tag Oil Q3 Average Net Daily Production 1,043 BOE/d, Down 9 Pct From Q2 Reuters Staff Feb 14 (Reuters) - Tag Oil Ltd: * TAG OIL REPORTS Q3 2018 RESULTS * TAG OIL - Q3 AVERAGE NET DAILY PRODUCTION 1,043 BOE/D, DOWN 9 PERCENT FROM Q2 2018 * TAG OIL LTD - REVENUES GENERATED FROM OIL AND GAS SALES INCREASED BY 6% FOR QUARTER ENDED DECEMBER 31, 2017, TO $6.4 MILLION VERSUS QUARTER ENDED SEPTEMBER 30, 2017 Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
